ity%20of%20Jakarta%E2%80%99s%20air%20and%20the%20urgency%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20candidates%20only%20touch%20on%20the%20general%20problem%20of%20green%20economics%20and%20solar%20panels.%20No%20one%20really%20seemed%20to%20educate%20the%20public%20about%20climate%20change%20or%20strongly%20declared%20promises%20to%20solve%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClimate%20change%20impacts%20are%20felt%20by%20everyone%2C%20from%20villages%20to%20cities.%20In%20cities%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fopinion%2F2023%2F11%2F25%2Fthe-right-to-clean-air.html%5C%22%3Eair%20pollution%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0affects%20residents%2C%20while%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kompas.id%2Fbaca%2Fenglish%2F2023%2F09%2F28%2Fen-bencana-kekeringan-yang-makin-meluas-di-indonesia%5C%22%3Edrought%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.antaranews.com%2Fnews%2F289152%2Fbmkg-warns-of-threat-of-el-nio-induced-crop-failure%5C%22%3Ecrop%20failure%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fu%3Eare%20continual%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20during%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kompas.id%2Fbaca%2Fenglish%2F2024%2F01%2F22%2Fen-analisis-debat-cawapres-kelestarian-lingkungan-jadi-isu-penting%5C%22%3Evice%20president%20candidates%E2%80%99%20debate%20on%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20did%20not%20touch%20on%20the%20main%20causes%20of%20climate%20change%20Indonesia%20is%20facing%2C%20such%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalforestwatch.org%2Fdashboards%2Fcountry%2FIDN%2F%5C%22%3Edeforestation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mongabay.com%2F2023%2F03%2Findonesian-campaigns-getting-money-from-illegal-logging-mining-watchdog-says%2F%5C%22%3Eillegal%20logging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Findonesia%2F2023%2F03%2F31%2Findonesias-electric-vehicle-ambitions-hinge-on-green-mining-drive.htm