0to%201%20pm.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20such%20an%20issue%20has%20occurred%20since%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20new%20trading%20platform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fmcx-glitch-latest-news-trading-likely-to-resume-at-this-time-after-technical-glitch-forces-shutdown%2Farticleshow%2F107652562.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Maglev%20Train%20That%20%26quot%3BLevitates%26quot%3B%20Above%20Track%20Breaks%20Own%20Speed%20Record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20China%20Aerospace%20Science%20and%20Industry%20Corporation%20(CASIC)%20has%20claimed%20that%20its%20new%20magnetically%20levitated%20(maglev)%20train%20has%20surpassed%20its%20previous%20record%20of%20623%20kilometres%20per%20hour%20(387miles%20per%20hour)%20during%20tests%20in%20a%20low-vacuum%20tube%20just%202%20km%20long.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20the%20exact%20speed%20reached%20by%20the%20train%20remains%20classified%2C%20the%20CASIC%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20had%20made%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20breakthrough%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20latest%20test.%20It%20also%20added%20that%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20ultra-fast%20hyperloop%20train%20achieved%20stable%20levitation%20while%20travelling%20in%20a%20low-vacuum%20tube.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20China%20could%20soon%20have%20a%20train%20that%20is%20as%20fast%20as%20a%20plane%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fscience%2Farticle%2F3250341%2Fchina-stakes-global-dominance-race-build-intelligent-ports%3Fcampaign%3D3250341%26module%3Dperpetual_scroll_1_RM%26pgtype%3Darticle%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20vehicle%20relies%20on%20maglev%20technology%2C%20which%20uses%20magnetism%20to%20propel%20the%2