million%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20270%20million%20people%20registering%20to%20vote%20across%20an%20archipelago%20made%20up%20of%20some%2017%2C000%20islands.%20The%20voters%20are%20spread%20across%20three%20time%20zones%2C%20from%20Papua%20in%20the%20east%20to%20the%20tip%20of%20Sumatra%20over%205%2C000%20kilometers%20(3%2C000%20miles)%20away%20in%20the%20west.%20Young%20people%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20registered%20voters%2C%20with%20some%2055%25%20of%20them%20aged%20between%2017%20and%2040%2C%20according%20to%20the%20General%20Elections%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncumbent%20President%20Joko%20Widodo%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Jokowi%2C%20is%20finishing%20his%20second%20term%20in%20office%20and%20cannot%20run%20again%20because%20of%20term%20limits.%20This%20year%E2%80%99s%20vote%20will%20thus%20lead%20to%C2%A0the%20first%20change%20in%20leadership%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20presidential%20candidates%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20candidates%20are%20going%20to%20succeed%20Jokowi%20as%20president%3A%20Ganjar%20Pranowo%20and%20Anies%20Baswedan%2C%20both%20former%20governors%20in%20their%2050s%2C%20and%20Prabowo%20Subianto%2C%20the%20current%20defense%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubianto%20is%20a%2072-year-old%20former%20army%20special%20forces%20commander%20who%20is%20running%20for%20the%20top%20job%20for%20a%20third%20time.%20He%20lost%20to%20Jokowi%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20To%20cement%20his%20chances%20this%20time%20round%2C%20Subianto%20has%20roped%20in%20the%20hugely%20popular%20president%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Gibran%20Rakabuming%20Raka%2C%20as%20his%20running%20mate%20for%20vice%20president.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0The%20candidacy%20of%C2%A036-year-old%20Raka%2C%20who%20is%20half%20Subianto%E2%80%99s%20age%20and%20currently%20serving%20as%20mayor%20in%20Surakarta%20city%2C%20is%20seen%20by%20many%20analysts%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%C2%A0secure%20more%20votes%20from%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubianto%20also%20hails%20from%20an%20elite%20political%20family.%20He%20was%20once%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20Suharto%2C%20a%20military%20dictator%20who%20was%20ousted%20from%20power%20in%201998%20after%20over%20three%20decades%20of%20rule.%C2%A0%20Subianto%20is%20accused%20of%20rights%20abuses%20while%20serving%20as%20a%20military%20chief%20during%20the%20dying%20days%20of%20the%20Suharto%20dictatorship.%20The%20allegations%20are%20unproven%2C%20and%20Prabowo%20has%20always%20denied%20any%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanjar%20Pranowo%2C%20another%20candidate%2C%20is%20a%20former%20governor%20of%20Central%20Java%20Province.%C2%A0%20His%20presidential%20bid%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20Indonesian%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Struggle%20(PDI-P).%20Pranowo%20has%20announced%20incumbent%20Cabinet%20minister%20Mahfud%20Md%20as%20his%20running%20mate.%20Pranowo%20adopted%20the%20political%20style%20of%20President%20Widodo%20by%20trying%20to%20gain%20sympathy%20from%20grassroots%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20presidential%20hopeful%20is%20Anies%20Baswedan%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20the%20Indonesian%20capital%2C%20Jakarta.%20His%20running%20mate%20is%20Muhaimin%20Iskandar%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Islamic%20National%20Awakening%20Party%20(PKB)%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20Islamic%20parties%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%20In%202017%2C%20Baswedan%20ran%20for%20governor%20of%20Jakarta%20against%20Basuki%20Tjahaja%20Purnama%2C%20who%20is%20of%20Chinese%20heritage.%20Baswedan%20won%20the%20election%20%E2%80%94%20while%20his%20competitor%20was%20sentenced%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20blaspheming%20the%20Quran%20during%20one%20of%20his%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20latest%20surveys%20by%20Litbang%20Kompas%2C%20an%20independent%20research%20organization%2C%20Subianto%20is%20enjoying%20a%20considerable%20lead%20over%20the%20other%20two%20candidates%2C%20with%20about%2039%25%20of%20voters%20polled%20backing%20him%20compared%20to%2018%25%20for%20Pranowo%20and%20around%2016%25%20for%20Baswedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20key%20issues%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20presidential%20hopefuls%20have%20made%20similar%20pledges%20on%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20welfare.%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20decade%20in%20office%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20stability%20and%20growth%20for%C2%A0Southeast%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20economy.%20And%20the%20three%20contenders%20have%20pledged%20to%20continue%20most%20of%20his%20initiatives%2C%20including%20boosting%20mining%2C%20expanding%20social%20welfare%20and%20continuing%20work%20on%20building%20a%20%2432%20billion%20(%E2%82%AC29.7%20billion)%20new%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidates%20have%20set%20ambitious%20economic%20expansion%20targets%20and%20pledged%20to%20create%20millions%20of%20jobs%2C%20without%20giving%20out%20specific%20details%20as%20to%20how%20they%20will%20reach%20these%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20can%20vote%20and%20when%20can%20we%20expect%20the%20results%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20Indonesian%20citizens%20who%20are%2017%20or%20older%20can%20vote.%C2%A0%20Following%20decades%20of%20authoritarian%20rule%2C%20Indonesia%20embraced%20democracy%20in%201998%20and%20adopted%20a%20national%20philosophy%20of%20equality%20and%20national%20unity%20called%20Pancasila%2C%20which%20is%20enshrined%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20Muslim-majority%20country%2C%20it%20is%20constitutionally%20a%20secular%20state%20with%20a%20separation%20of%20religion%20and%20state.%20Nevertheless%2C%20political%20parties%20often%20employ%20religion%20in%20their%20campaign%20tactics.%C2%A0%20The%20nation%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20plays%20a%20relatively%20subordinate%20role%20in%20decision-making%2C%20with%20policy-making%20power%20resting%20with%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20election%20rules%2C%20presidential%20candidates%20need%2050%25%20of%20the%20overall%20vote%20and%20at%20least%2020%25%20of%20votes%20in%20each%20province%20to%20win%20the%20vote.%C2%A0%20To%20enter%20parliament%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20for%20their%20part%2C%20need%20to%20secure%204%25%20of%20the%20vote.%C2%A0%20A%20preliminary%20result%20from%20the%20elections%20commission%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20announced%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20February%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20official%20outcome%20could%20take%20as%20long%20as%2035%20days%20to%20be%20made%20public%2C%20if%20no%20presidential%20contender%20gets%20over%2050%25%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20the%20contest%20goes%20to%20a%20second%20and%20final%20round%20between%20the%20top%20two%20in%20June.%20The%20new%20president%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKomnas%20HAM%2C%20an%20independent%20human%20rights%20body%2C%20said%20there%20are%2017%20groups%20of%20people%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20face%20challenges%20when%20exercising%20their%20right%20to%20vote.%20They%20include%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20LGBTQ%20communities%2C%20indigenous%20communities%20and%20religious%20minorities%2C%20among%20others.In%20North%20Sumatra%20province%2C%20Komnas%20HAM%20found%20instances%20of%20discrimination%20against%20LGBTQ%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20the%20LGBTQ%20community%20felt%20increasingly%20insecure%20(to%20vote)%20because%20there%20was%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20regional%20leadership%20declaring%20Medan%20as%20an%20LGBTQ-free%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pramono%20Ubaid%20Tanthowi%2C%20a%20Komnas%20HAM%20official%2C%20was%20quoted%20by%20local%20media%20outlet%20%3Cem%3Edetik.com%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20by%20people%20with%20disabilities%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20low%2C%20said%20Kikin%20P.%20Tarigan%20of%20the%20Indonesian%20National%20Commission%20for%20Disabilities%2C%20pointing%20to%20inadequate%20efforts%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20election%20commission%20to%20register%20people%20with%20disabilities%20as%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%2Fa-68230075%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112512%2Fimage-1825.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Voters%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20Muslim-majority%20country%20will%20elect%20a%20new%20president%20and%20parliament%20on%20February%2014.%20It%20will%20mark%20the%20first%20change%20of%20leadership%20in%20a%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infrastructure%20major%20L%26amp%3BT%20bags%20'significant'%20orders%20in%20Middle%20East%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-09%2F29%2Ffull%2F1632903331-5748.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-bags-significant-orders-in-middle-east-124021300466_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infrastructure%20major%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20its%20hydrocarbon%20division%20has%20bagged%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20orders%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20client%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcomp