n%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20response%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20this%20criticism%20is%20to%20hold%20roadshows%20%E2%80%9Cdemonstrating%E2%80%9D%20EVMs%20and%20naively%20bombarding%20the%20public%20with%20reams%20of%20%E2%80%98Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%20(FAQs)%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobally%2C%20there%20are%20five%20types%20of%20voting%20systems%20in%20use%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Paper%20ballots%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20EVMs%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20EVMs%20with%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E4.%20Machine-readable%20paper%20ballots%2C%20and%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E5.%20Internet-based%20voting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20started%20with%20the%20first%20type%2C%20then%20went%20on%20to%20the%20second%20and%20is%20now%20using%20the%20third.%20While%20paper%20ballots%20comply%20with%20principles%20of%20democracy%2C%20EVMs%20do%20not.%20These%20principles%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20process%20should%20be%20transparent%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20the%20general%20public%20should%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20that%20their%20vote%20is%20correctly%20recorded%20and%20counted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20and%20counting%20process%20should%20be%20publicly%20auditable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOrdinary%20citizens%20should%20be%20able%20to%20check%20the%20essential%20steps%20in%20the%20voting%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20should%20be%20examinability%20and%20verifiability%20of%20the%20voting%20process%2C%20counting%20of%20votes%20and%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20election%20process%20should%20not%20only%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20but%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20should%20be%20in%20full%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20voting%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20can%20be%20better%20explained%20by%20comparing%20the%20process%20under%20the%20paper-ballot%20voting%20system%20and%20EVM%20voting.%20Let%20us%20do%20it%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20an%20ordinary%20voter%20who%20is%20transferring%20his%20sovereignty%20for%20five%20years%20to%20their%20elected%20representative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdemocracy-voting-evm-vvpat-modi-election%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Will%20of%20the%20People%20to%20the%20Whim%20of%20the%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20under%20the%20paper-ballot%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBallot-box%20is%20kept%20inside%20a%20secluded%20voting%20compartment%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20enters%20the%20polling%20station%20and%2C%20after%20verification%2C%20is%20handed%20over%20the%20ballot-paper%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20examine%20it%20to%20check%20whether%20their%20candidate%20and%20the%20corresponding%20symbol%20is%20on%20the%20ballot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20goes%20in%20to%20the%20voting%20compartment%20where%20the%20ballot-box%20is%20kept%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20affixes%20the%20stamp%20on%20the%20candidate%2Fsymbol%20of%20their%20choice%20and%20puts%20it%20inside%20the%20ballot-box%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ECounting%20is%20done%20manually%2C%20at%20the%20counting%20table%2C%20by%20physically%20sorting%20out%20the%20votes%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20(RO)%20and%20candidates%E2%80%99%20agents%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20counting%20table%20has%20one%20tray%20for%20each%20candidate%2C%20one%20for%20%E2%80%98doubtful%E2%80%99%20votes%20and%20one%20for%20%E2%80%98rejected%E2%80%99%20ones%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20verifying%2Fauditing%20process%2C%20votes%20are%20bundled%20(25%20each)%20and%20tallying%20is%20done%20between%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20to%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%20then%20counted%20by%20placing%20the%20votes%20in%20respective%20trays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAgents%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20each%20vote%20as%20it%20is%20placed%20in%20respective%20trays.%20Before%20the%20final%20tally%2C%20%E2%80%98Rejected%E2%80%99%20votes%20get%20re-confirmed%20and%20%E2%80%98doubtful%E2%80%99%20votes%20are%20reviewed%20with%20the%20agents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20disputes%20are%20resolved%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20if%20need%20be%2C%20with%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20RO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20paper%20ballot%20system%2C%20voters%20can%20check%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20ballot-paper%2C%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20verify%20whether%20it%20has%20been%20correctly%20marked.%20This%20provides%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20that%20one%20has%20transferred%20the%20sovereignty%20to%20the%20candidate%20of%20their%20choice.%20In%20case%20of%20electoral%20dispute%2C%20physical%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20vote%20for%20authentication%20is%20possible.%20Vote%20counting%20is%20open%20and%20transparent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20under%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EEVM%20comprises%20two%20units%20%E2%80%94%20a%20ballot%20unit%20(BU)%20containing%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20and%20symbols%20against%20each%20button%20and%20a%20control%20unit%20(CU)%20containing%20the%20memory%20and%20display%20component%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20voter-verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20relates%20to%20the%20BU%20and%20the%20CU.%20The%20BU%2C%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%20are%20interconnected%20by%20an%20insulated%20cable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CU%20is%20with%20the%20polling%20officer%2C%20while%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20are%20placed%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20a%20voter%20enters%2C%20the%20polling%20officer%20presses%20the%20BU%20button.%20As%20the%20green%20light%20glows%2C%20it%20enables%20the%20voter%20to%20cast%20the%20vote%20by%20pressing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20BU%20against%20the%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20symbol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EInstantly%2C%20the%20serial%20number%2C%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20appears%20on%20the%20window%20of%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20remaining%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20seven%20seconds%2C%20a%20loud%20beep%20emanates%20from%20the%20CU%2C%20indicating%20the%20vote%20is%20cast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20counting%20of%20votes%2C%20the%20counting%20official%20presses%20counting%20button%20on%20the%20CU%20that%20displays%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20against%20each%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20verification%2C%20auditing%20and%20dispute%20resolution%20on%20the%20spot%20before%20final%20results%20are%20announced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftn-seshan-election-commissioner%5C%22%3ET.%20N.%20Seshan%2C%20the%20Unyielding%20Force%20That%20Cleansed%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20absolute%20transparency%20of%20the%20paper-ballots%2C%20there%20is%20total%20opaqueness%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20system.%20Everything%20is%20done%20inside%20a%20machine%2C%20in%20a%20non-transparent%20manner%2C%20without%20examination%2C%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20as%20to%20whether%20sovereignty%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice.%20All%20that%20the%20voter%20has%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20look%20at%20a%20slip%20for%20seven%20seconds.%20They%20have%20no%20assurance%20that%20the%20slip%20was%20counted%20or%20got%20manipulated%20between%20VVPAT%20and%20EVM.%20Under%20the%20EVM%20system%2C%20all%20that%20a%20voter%20does%20is%20to%20press%20a%20button%2C%20see%20a%20light%20and%20hear%20a%20sound.%20They%20have%20no%20idea%20whether%20the%20vote%20has%20been%20registered%20and%2C%20if%20so%2C%20to%20which%20candidate.%20There%20is%20no%20transparency%20even%20during%20counting%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%20and%20professionals%20say%20that%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20EVM%20(BU-VVPAT-CU)%20units%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20standalone%20machines%20having%20one-time%20programmable%20chips%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20true.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20to%20EVMs%20using%20an%20external%20device%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20and%20finalisation%20of%20candidate%20list.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20Manual%20states%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd.%20(BEL)%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(ECIL)%20engineers%20are%20to%20use%20a%20device%20called%20Symbol%20Loading%20Unit%20(SLU)%20to%20electronically%20upload%20these%20details%20to%20the%20VVPAT.%20The%20same%20manual%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20devices%20need%20not%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20strong%20room%20along%20with%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20and%20are%20to%20be%20released%20to%20the%20engineers%20immediately%20after%20the%20poll%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20leaving%20them%20outside%20of%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20ROs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20wired%20connection%20of%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20to%20an%20external%20device%20not%20maintained%20within%20the%20RO%2FDistrict%20Election%20Officers%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20announced%2C%20candidate%20sequence%20is%20firmed%20up%2C%20and%20second%20randomisation%20and%20booth%20allotment%20of%20EVMs%20finalised%2C%C2%A0%20makes%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20practices%20in%20conducting%20elections%20extremely%20suspect.%20This%20has%20exposed%20the%20voting%20and%20counting%20to%20manipulation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERule%2056(D)(4)(b)%20of%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%2C%20provides%20that%20the%20count%20of%20VVPATs%20shall%20prevail%20over%20the%20count%20reflected%20in%20EVMs%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20votes%20displayed%20on%20the%20control%20unit%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20paper%20slips%2C%20amend%20the%20result%20sheet%20in%20Form%2020%20as%20per%20the%20paper%20slips%20count.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20rule%20is%20a%20statutory%20admission%20of%20the%20position%20in%20law%20and%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20finally%20the%20VVPAT%20which%20accurately%20captures%20the%20will%20of%20the%20voter%20and%20that%20variance%20or%20errors%20in%20the%20results%20captured%20in%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20for%20any%20given%20reason.%20Given%20the%20statutory%20acknowledgement%2C%20it%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20and%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%2014%20to%20not%20to%20fully%20count%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EECI%20has%20lost%20control%20under%20the%20electronic%20system%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20ballot%20paper%20system%2C%20ECI%20had%20full%20control%20and%20supervision%20over%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20ballot-boxes%2C%20printing%20of%20ballot-papers%2C%20its%20despatch%20and%20counting%20of%20votes.%20That%20is%20not%20the%20case%20with%20EVMs%20that%20contains%20two%20EEPROMS%20(Electrically%20Erasable%20and%20Programmable%20Memory)%20inside%20the%20control%20unit%20in%20which%20the%20voting%20data%20is%20stored.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20manufacturers%20of%20EVMs%2C%20are%20not%20under%20the%20control%20or%20supervision%20of%20ECI.%20They%20are%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20respective%20ministries%C2%A0%20and%20the%20day-to-day%20administration%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20packed%20with%20ruling%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20functionaries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20entities%20share%20the%20confidential%20software%20programme%20with%20foreign%20chip%20manufacturers%20to%20copy%20it%20on%20to%20micro-controllers%20used%20in%20the%20EVMs.%20When%20these%20foreign%20companies%20deliver%20micro-controllers%20fused%20with%20software%20code%20to%20the%20EVM%20manufacturers%2C%20neither%20the%20manufacturer%20nor%20the%20ECI%20officials%20can%20read%20back%20their%20contents%20because%20they%20are%20locked.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20EVM%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20any%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%20that%20are%20paramount%20which%20makes%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20imperative%20for%20India%20to%20return%20to%20the%20paper%20ballot.%20The%20only%20grievance%20against%20this%20system%20is%20that%20there%20used%20to%20be%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot-stuffing.%20This%20was%20when%20the%20supervision%2C%20security%2C%20transportation%20and%20communication%20systems%20were%20primitive%20%E2%80%93%20not%20the%20case%20any%20longer.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20senior%20election%20officials%2C%20ECI%20observers%2C%20police%20and%20flying%20squads%20can%20observe%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20polling%20booths%20live%20through%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20can%20intervene%20instantly%20in%20the%20event%20of%20any%20mischief.%20Besides%2C%20sensitive%20booths%20are%20guarded%20by%20armed%20police%20with%20orders%20to%20shoot%20in%20case%20of%20any%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot%20stuffing.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20reason%20for%20the%20ECI%20not%20to%20comply%20with%20this%20demand.%20Any%20amendment%20to%20election%20law%20can%20be%20notified%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%20through%20ordinance.%20Logistics%20of%20procuring%20ballot%20boxes%20and%20other%20material%20could%20be%20done%20in%20couple%20of%20weeks%20because%20they%20are%20being%20used%20for%20panchayat%20and%20local%20bodies%20elections%20and%20are%20continuously%20being%20manufactured.%20Trained%20personnel%20are%20also%20available.%20Ballot%20papers%20will%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20be%20printed%20only%20after%20the%20candidate%20list%20is%20finalised.%20All%20that%20is%20needed%20is%20to%20shortlist%20printing%20presses%20and%20have%20them%20cleared%20after%20security%20checks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20without%20playing%20%E2%80%98marketing%20agents%E2%80%99%20for%20EVMs%2C%20ECI%20should%20heed%20the%20cry%20of%20the%20people%20and%20return%20to%20paper%20ballots%20to%20save%20democracy%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20Officer.%20He%20is%20Coordinator%20of%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EElectoral%20Democracy%E2%80%94An%20Inquiry%20into%20the%20Fairness%20and%20Integrity%20of%20Elections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F05084439%2F2022_12img04_Dec_2022_PTI12_04_.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20trust%20in%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20has%20never%20been%20lower%20than%20it%20is%20today%20and%20there's%20a%20good%20reason%20why.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BSE%20Sensex%20surges%20450%20points%2C%20Nifty50%20above%2021%2C700%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107651550%2Cimgsize-100270.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-today-bse-sensex-nifty50-february-13-2024-bombay-stock-exchange-dalal-street-msci-inflation%2Farticleshow%2F107651334.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20today%3A%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty50%20surged%20in%20trade%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20investors%20awaited%20crucial%20US%20inflation%20data.%20The%20easing%20domestic%20inflation%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20five%20Indian%20stocks%20into%20a%20key%20MSCI%20index%20boosted%20market%20sentiment.%20At%2011%3A54%20AM%2C%20BSE%20Sensex%20was%20trading%20at%2071%2C517.27%2C%20up%20over%20440%20points%20or%200.63%25.%20Nifty50%20was%20at%2021%2C725.65%2C%20up%20over%20100%20points%20or%200.51%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-today-bse-sensex-nifty50-february-13-2024-bombay-stock-exchange-dalal-street-msci-inflation%2Farticleshow%2F107651334.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Systemic%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20an%20Oppressive%20TMC%20and%20Not%20Much%20Recourse%3A%20What%20Sandeshkhali%20Villagers%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112718%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.26-AM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandeshkhali%20(Bengali)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Since%20last%20week%2C%20extraordinary%20sights%20of%20protest%20and%20political%20developments%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20a%20village%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20North%2024%20Parganas%20that%20had%20largely%20been%20out%20of%20the%20radar%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3Enews%20of%20an%20attack%20on%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20by%20a%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%20broke%20last%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20protests%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20February%208%20are%20not%20directly%20linked%20to%20the%20tussle%20between%20state%20and%20Union%20government.%20Instead%2C%20they%20concern%20hundreds%20women%20who%20have%20alleged%20that%20top%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20the%20area%20have%20unleashed%20a%20%E2%80%98reign%20of%20terror%E2%80%99%20including%20consistent%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20assault%20against%20local%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20women%20have%20named%20TMC%20strongman%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20incidentally%20absconding%20since%20the%20ED%20visit%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20aides%20Sibaprasad%20alias%20Sibu%20Hazra%2C%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20many%20women%20have%20spoken%20to%20various%20reporters%20and%20described%20instances%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20by%20TMC%20leaders.%20Some%20have%20set%20fire%20to%20properties%20belonging%20to%20TMC%20leaders.%20Police%20have%20largely%20not%20intervened%2C%20however%2C%20internet%20has%20been%20shutdown%20and%20Section%20144%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20cable%20operators%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20pause%20services%20there.%20The%20area%20office%20of%20the%20TMC%20is%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%20Police%20are%20stationed%20at%20regular%20intervals%20throughout%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reporter%20saw%20police%20give%20chase%20to%20a%20woman%20when%20a%20few%20villagers%20intervened%20and%20escorted%20her%20to%20safety.%20According%20to%20locals%2C%20she%20had%20been%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20ongoing%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919-300x175.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919-1024x598.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696876%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20protesting%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20of%20horrific%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20two%20women%20who%20recounted%20horrific%20abuse.%20Both%20have%20asked%20for%20their%20names%20to%20be%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20brought%20me%20into%20the%20party%20office%2C%20where%20a%20group%20of%20people%20were%20drinking.%20For%20the%20next%20one%20and%20half%20days%2C%20two%20of%20them%20tortured%20me%20in%20the%20party%20office%20itself.%20I%20was%20told%20that%20my%20husband%20would%20not%20%E2%80%98take%20me%20back%E2%80%99%20after%20this%20and%20so%20I%20should%20stay%20on%20with%20the%20men%20in%20the%20room%20%E2%80%93%20that%20they%20would%20give%20me%20a%20government%20job%20eventually.%20They%20said%20they%20would%20place%20my%20husband%E2%80%99s%20severed%20head%20on%20my%20palms%20if%20I%20complained%20about%20what%20they%20had%20done%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20woman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20that%20local%20girls%20and%20women%20are%20terrified%20of%20attention%20from%20them.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20woman%20found%20attractive%20by%20a%20TMC%20leader%20would%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20party%20office%20and%20leaders%20would%20take%20turns%20to%20rape%20her.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EYour%20caste%20or%20religion%20won%E2%80%99t%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20left%20the%20area%2C%20she%20said.%20And%20some%20other%20survivors%20have%20indeed%20been%20abandoned%20by%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112521%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112521%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112521%2FUntitled-design-12-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112521%2FUntitled-design-12-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696869%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20who%20spoke%20of%20systemic%20abuse%20against%20them%20by%20local%20leaders%2C%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20in%20her%20mid-fifties%20said%20that%20in%20%3Cspan%3E2021%2C%20the%20women%20of%20the%20area%20sent%20a%20mass%20petition%20detailing%20all%20the%20cases%20of%20rape%20and%20torture%20of%20local%20women%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20by%20post.%20%E2%80%9CThings%20did%20not%20improve.%20Police%20started%20threatening%20us%20for%20acting%20smart%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20that%20the%20wanton%20crimes%20against%20local%20women%20are%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20scheme%20where%20rights%20are%20continuously%20infringed%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20robbed%20of%20our%20dignity.%20When%20the%20men%20in%20our%20families%20protested%2C%20TMC%20cadres%20and%20police%20mercilessly%20beat%20them%20up.%20Farmland%20was%20captured%20without%20farmers%E2%80%99%20consent%20and%20turned%20into%20fisheries.%20No%20one%20got%20any%20compensation.%20Even%20allowances%20and%20money%20for%20working%20for%20government%20projects%20were%20forcibly%20taken%20away%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20295px)%2085vw%2C%20295px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112610%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.28-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22295%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112610%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.28-AM.jpeg%20826w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112610%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.28-AM-212x300.jpeg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112610%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.28-AM-724x1024.jpeg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22418%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20poster%20%E2%80%98welcoming%E2%80%99%20Shahjahan.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShahjahan%20Sheikh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20local%20said%20that%20rising%20awareness%20of%20how%20the%20state%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Clooting%E2%80%9D%20people%E2%80%99s%20money%20is%20why%20internet%20has%20been%20shut%20down.%20%E2%80%9CYouth%20are%20able%20to%20look%20up%20how%20%3Cspan%3E%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20done%20work%20worth%20crores%20which%20have%20come%20to%20naught%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20Sheikh%20is%20very%20much%20the%20centre%20of%20all%20things%20Sandeshkhali.%20It%20is%20to%20search%20his%20house%20that%20ED%20officials%20arrived%20in%20the%20village%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20public%20distribution%20system%20scam.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts%20have%20remained%20unknown%20despite%20multiple%20summons%20and%20a%20lookout%20notice%20by%20the%20ED.%20His%20legal%20team%20has%20sought%20court%20approval%20for%20bail%20on%20several%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDidi%20is%20protecting%20him.%20He%20is%20being%20sheltered%20by%20the%20police%20and%20the%20administration.%20They%20might%20want%20to%20diffuse%20the%20anger%20by%20arresting%20one%20or%20two%20people%2C%20but%20the%20main%20culprit%20is%20still%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20woman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Kacharipara%20part%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20another%20villager%20says%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20corruption%20in%20the%20village%20%E2%80%9Cstarted%20soon%20after%20Trinamool%20came%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYoung%20boys%20of%2015-16%20years%20were%20lured%20with%20alcohol.%20The%20biker%20gang%20of%20the%20party%20picked%20up%20our%20children%20from%20school%2C%20gave%20them%20guns%2C%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20take%20part%20in%20violence.%20The%20situation%20has%20worsened%20since%202018.%20They%20looted%20money%2C%20land%20and%20our%20women%E2%80%99s%20honour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20villager%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%3A%20Arrests%2C%20re-arrests%20and%20no%20%E2%80%98rape%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20three%20being%20accused%20of%20such%20crimes%20%E2%80%93%20Shahjahan%2C%20Uttam%20Sardar%20and%20Sibu%20Hazra%20%E2%80%93%20are%20members%20of%20the%20TMC-run%20Zilla%20Parishad.%20While%20Uttam%20won%20uncontested%2C%20Shahjahan%20and%20Sibu%20received%2099.9%25%20and%2098%25%20of%20total%20votes%20in%20the%20latest%20panchayat%20polls.%20Many%20believe%20that%20such%20figures%20indicate%20irregularities%20in%20the%20voting%20process%20rather%20than%20the%20mass%20support%20they%20command.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFaced%20with%20massive%20outrage%20from%20across%20the%20state%2C%20TMC%20on%20February%2010%20suspended%20Uttam%20for%20six%20years.%20For%20locals%2C%20this%20is%20little%20more%20than%20a%20token%20gesture.%20While%20Uttam%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20soon%20after%20that%2C%20police%20also%20arrested%20former%20Sandeshkhali%20MLA%20and%20CPI(M)%20state%20committee%20member%20Nirapada%20Sardar%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20February%2011%2C%20from%20Kolkata%2C%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Sibu%20who%20is%20still%20absconding.%20In%20the%20mean%20time%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Bikash%20Sinha%20was%20also%20held.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20were%20produced%20in%20the%20Basirhat%20court%20a%20day%20ago.%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Uttam%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bikash%20got%20bail%2C%20but%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Nirapada%2C%20did%20not.%C2%A0%20BJP%20and%20TMC%20workers%C2%A0%20outside%20the%20court%20welcomed%20the%20two%20amidst%20much%20fanfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20afterwards%2C%20police%20re-arrested%20Sinha%20over%20what%20they%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20old%20case%E2%80%9D.%20When%20protests%20led%20by%20local%20BJP%20workers%20appeared%20to%20go%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20and%20in%20dramatic%20scenes%2C%20Uttam%20was%20then%20brought%20back%20and%20re-arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20constituted%20a%2010-member%20team%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20DIG-rank%20woman%20IPS%20officer%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20The%20team%20will%20begin%20groundwork%20from%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Barasat%20Range%20DIG%20Sumit%20Kumar%20told%20reporters%20that%20four%20complaints%20have%20yet%20been%20filed%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20them%20mention%20rape.%20If%20we%20get%20such%20a%20complaint%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action.%20We%20are%20investigating%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20respond%20to%20this%20claim%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20had%20spoken%20to%20The%20Wire%20of%20sexual%20assault%20said%20that%20she%20had%20grown%20so%20used%20to%20seeing%20policemen%20in%20public%20places%20with%20the%20accused%20TMC%20leaders%20that%20she%20does%20not%20expect%20behaviour%20to%20the%20contrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20police%20have%20also%20allegedly%20stopped%20groups%20led%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20to%20the%20village%2C%20although%20the%20governor%2C%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%20has%20visited%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wire%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Basirhat%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Dr.%20Hossain%20Mehedi%20Rehman%2C%20requesting%20various%20details%20on%20what%20the%20arrests%20and%20re-arrests%20were%20on%20the%20basis%20of%2C%20and%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20police%20action%20initially.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20once%20there%20is%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20boy%20(face%20blurred%20to%20protect%20identity%20as%20he%20is%20a%20minor)%20points%20to%20a%20fishery%20created%20allegedly%20after%20illegally%20occupying%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20land%2C%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20land%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2011%2C%20as%20this%20reporter%20chatted%20with%20residents%20on%20Khulna%20Island%2C%20some%20men%20on%20bikes%20suddenly%20appeared%20to%20be%20patrolling%20the%20area.%20A%20few%20villagers%20grew%20alert.%20One%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBe%20careful.%20Parimal%20Mridha%20and%20Santosh%20have%20heard%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20talking%20to%20you.%20They%20might%20torture%20us%20again.%E2%80%9D%20Both%20are%20local%20TMC%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVillagers%20pointed%20to%20a%20massive%20fishery.%20Once%20known%20as%20Majherpara%2C%20the%20land%20which%20used%20to