0secure%20Indian%20interests.%20In%20one%20stroke%2C%20Modi%20has%20underscored%20how%20he%20remains%20key%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-supervised-developments-centre-on-return-of-navy-veterans-from-qatar-5042929%5C%22%3EIndia's%20rising%20global%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20something%20his%20critics%20have%20continued%20to%20challenge%20since%202014%20despite%20all%20the%20evidence%20to%20the%20contrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20forget%20how%20tense%20a%20time%20it%20was%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-are-the-8-indians-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-and-what-is-the-case-against-them-4517939%5C%22%3EQatari%20court%20had%20sentenced%20the%20men%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20There%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20despair%20about%20their%20future%2C%20and%20in%20retaliation%2C%20there%20were%20many%20who%20were%20quick%20to%20suggest%20that%20New%20Delhi%20should%20renounce%20its%20ties%20with%20Doha.%20Qatar's%20decision%20to%20challenge%20the%20foundations%20of%20an%20essentially%20strong%20relationship%20had%20begun%20to%20provoke%20a%20rethink%20in%20India%20about%20the%20future%20sustainability%20of%20this%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20PM-Level%20Talks%20Became%20Necessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20expressed%20its%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20shock%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20verdict%20and%20had%20explored%20all%20possible%20legal%20and%20diplomatic%20options-from%20high-level%20political%20engagement%20to%20moving%20through%20the%20appeals%20process%2C%20and%20even%20invoking%20the%20provisions%20of%20a%202015%20pact%20on%20the%20transfer%20of%20sentenced%20prisoners.%20But%20the%20road%20ahead%20was%20difficult%20and%20it%20required%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvictory-of-pm-modis-diplomatic-efforts-bjp-on-relief-in-death-row-in-qatar-4759034%5C%22%3Edeft%20diplomacy%20and%20leadership%20from%20the%20very%20top%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fnation%2Fpm-modi-meets-qatars-ruler-discusses-well-being-of-indian-community%5C%22%3Eprime%20ministerial-level%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20the%20key.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20suggest%20that%20India%20has%20leverage%20in%20its%20ties%20with%20Qatar%2C%20but%20deploying%20it%20effectively%20requires%20a%20leadership%20that%20is%20willing%20to%20push%20for%20concrete%20outcomes.%20Modi's%20willingness%20to%20put%20himself%20out%20there%20is%20a%20key%20variable%20that%20made%20a%20positive%20outcome%20possible.%20For%20any%20leader%2C%20such%20a%20move%20is%20full%20of%20risks%2C%20as%20a%20failure%20would%20have%20led%20to%20questions%20being%20raised%20about%20Modi's%20global%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Modi%20met%20the%20Emir%20of%20Qatar%2C%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamid%20Al%20Thani%2C%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP-28%20meeting%20in%20Dubai%20last%20December%2C%20after%20which%20the%20sentences%20of%20the%20eight%20Indian%20navy%20officials%20were%20reduced.%20It%20was%20a%20sign%20that%20things%20were%20moving%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20And%20then%2C%20last%20week%2C%20India%20and%20Qatar%20signed%20a%20major%20deal%20that%20will%20secure%20exports%20of%20Qatari%20liquified%20natural%20gas%20to%20India%20until%20the%20end%20of%202048.%20This%20builds%20on%20a%2025-year%20agreement%20that%20was%20due%20to%20expire%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EGood%20Ties%20Are%20Important%20For%20Both%20India%20%26amp%3B%20Qatar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Qatar%20do%20enjoy%20strong%20economic%20ties%2C%20with%20the%20Gulf%20nation%20being%20the%20largest%20supplier%20of%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20to%20India%2C%20accounting%20for%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20its%20LNG%20imports.%20Also%2C%20an%20Indian%20diaspora%20of%20around%20840%2C000%20sustains%20Qatar's%20labour%20force.%20For%20Qatar%2C%20building%20robust%20ties%20with%20an%20emerging%20economic%20power%20like%20India%20has%20been%20a%20priority%20as%20it%20seeks%20diversification%20in%20its%20external%20relationships%2C%20while%20for%20New%20Delhi%2C%20it%20has%20been%20about%20strengthening%20its%20partnership%20with%20a%20Gulf%20state%20that%20punches%20above%20its%20weight%20in%20the%20region%20and%20beyond.%20There%20is%20a%20reason%20why%20when%20Qatar%20was%20isolated%20and%20feeling%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20Saudi-led%20blockade%20in%202017-2021%2C%20India%20continued%20with%20its%20economic%20engagement%20with%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20partnership%20that%20many%20in%20India%20had%20begun%20to%20question%20after%20the%20diplomatic%20challenge%20posed%20by%20the%20action%20against%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans.%20Modi%20has%20managed%20to%20salvage%20this%20key%20relationship%20by%20reminding%20both%20the%20Qataris%20and%20the%20Indians%20that%20there%20is%20value%20in%20preserving%20the%20sanctity%20of%20their%20partnership.%20Qatar's%20decision%20came%20on%20the%20day%20when%20Modi%20was%20embarking%20on%20his%20two%20day%20trip%20to%20the%20UAE%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20first%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20further%20underscoring%20how%20transformative%20his%20leadership%20has%20been%20in%20shaping%20India's%20engagement%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Success%20Story%20For%20The%20Modi%20Government%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20region%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20success%20stories%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20foreign%20policy%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20With%20some%20deft%20diplomatic%20footwork%20and%20a%20newfound%20nimbleness%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20managed%20to%20build%20remarkably%20strong%20ties%20with%20the%20Arab%20states%20in%20the%20Gulf.%20Looking%20beyond%20just%20energy%20ties%20and%20diaspora%20linkages%2C%20the%20Indian%20approach%20to%20the%20region%20has%20assumed%20a%20strategic%20character%2C%20making%20way%20for%20a%20wider%20regional%20policy%20response%20instead%20of%20merely%20bilaterals%2C%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20emergence%20of%20that%20I2U2%20(India%2C%20Israel%2C%20UAE%20and%20the%20US)%20minilateral.%20This%20converged%20in%20the%20high-profile%20announcement%20during%20last%20year's%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%2C%20a%20multi-modal%20transport%20and%20economic%20corridor%20connecting%20three%20geographies%2C%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20economic%20prosperity%20and%20bridging%20the%20infrastructure%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fitting%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20Modi%20will%20be%20visiting%20Doha%20too%20this%20week%20after%20the%20UAE%2C%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Qatar%20since%202016.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20reminder%20to%20both%20the%20Indians%20and%20the%20Qataris%20that%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20of%20Indian%20leaders%20for%20New%20Delhi's%20engagement%20with%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20that%20the%20region%20has%20reciprocated%20the%20gesture%20by%20recognising%20Modi's%20contribution%20to%20building%20a%20robust%20bilateral%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707805200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fefp1meno_modi-qatar-amir_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20by%20Qatar%20to%20free%20eight%20Indian%20navy%20veterans%20who%20were%20facing%20death%20sentences%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20distinct%20ability%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20forge%20strong%20personal%20bonds%20with%20global%20leaders%20to%20secure%20Indian%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Seeks%20Stadium%20To%20Detain%20Protesting%20Farmers%2C%20Delhi%20Minister%20Says%20No%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20march%20towards%20Delhi%20for%20a%20mega%20protest%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20has%20rejected%20the%20Centre's%20proposal%20to%20turn%20a%20stadium%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20to%20confine%20them.%20The%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20has%20said%20the%20farmers'%20demands%20are%20genuine%20and%20added%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20the%20right%20to%20peaceful%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%20are%20genuine.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Constitutional%20right%20of%20every%20citizen%20to%20make%20a%20peaceful%20protest.%20It%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20incorrect%20to%20arrest%20the%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20home%20minister%20Kailash%20Gehlot%20has%20said%20in%20a%20reply%20to%20the%20Centre's%20proposal%20to%20convert%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20stadium%20in%20Bawana%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20to%20detain%20the%20protesting%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Central%20government%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20should%20invite%20them%20over%20for%20talks%20and%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20of%20their%20genuine%20problems.%20Farmers%20of%20the%20country%20are%20our%20'annadata'%20and%20treating%20them%20in%20this%20way%20by%20arresting%20them%20would%20be%20like%20rubbing%20salt%20into%20their%20wounds.%20We%20cannot%20be%20a%20party%20to%20this%20decision%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20are%20protesting%20over%20several%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20their%20crops%2C%20pension%20and%20insurance%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20between%20the%20farmers%20and%20Centre%20have%20not%20made%20a%20breakthrough%20after%20several%20rounds%20of%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20fortress%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20from%20entering%20the%20city.%20Delhi's%20borders%20with%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20been%20sealed.%20From%20cement%20barriers%20to%20sandbags%20to%20tyre%20deflators%2C%20cops%20are%20going%20all-out%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20at%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20have%20started%20from%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20in%20Punjab%20and%20have%20said%20they%20plan%20to%20protest%20peacefully.%20The%20farmers%20have%20said%20they%20have%20no%20links%20with%20any%20political%20party.%20Asked%20about%20the%20massive%20preparation%20by%20police%20to%20stop%20their%20march%2C%20they%20replied%20they%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20once%20they%20reach%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20Munda%2C%20Minister%20for%20State%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers'%20Welfare%2C%20said%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers.%20%26quot%3BOn%20some%20issues%2C%20we%20will%20need%20to%20consult%20the%20states.%20We%20will%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20We%20are%20always%20ready%20to%20talk%20and%20find%20a%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20have%20clamped%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20a%20month%20in%20view%20of%20the%20protests.%20Large%20gatherings%20and%20any%20form%20of%20protest%20marches%20have%20been%20banned.%20Restrictions%20have%20also%20been%20imposed%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparations%20suggest%20that%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20determined%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20January%2026%2C%202021%20incident%20when%20protesting%20farmers%20clashed%20with%20police%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Delhi.%20They%20were%20then%20protesting%20against%20three%20farm%20laws%20that%20were%20later%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20many%20of%20the%20organisations%20part%20of%20the%202020-2021%20protest%20on%20Delhi%20borders%20are%20not%20participating%20in%20today's%20march.%20But%20they%20have%20warned%20that%20they%20will%20hit%20the%20streets%20if%20any%20farmer%20is%20manhandled.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707805140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F97q0e30g_nail-spikes-farmers_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrong-to-put-farmers-in-jail-arvind-kejriwal-rejects-centres-proposal-5048117%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20march%20towards%20Delhi%20for%20a%20mega%20protest%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20has%20rejected%20the%20Centre's%20proposal%20to%20turn%20a%20stadium%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20to%20confine%20them%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrong-to-put-farmers-in-jail-arvind-kejriwal-rejects-centres-proposal-