20information%20in%20your%20conversations%20or%20any%20data%20you%20wouldn't%20want%20a%20reviewer%20to%20see%20or%20Google%20to%20use%20to%20improve%20our%20products%2C%20services%2C%20and%20machine-learning%20technologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20one%20must%20avoid%20giving%20personal%20information%2C%20Google%20stated%20that%20once%20any%20conversation%20has%20been%20reviewed%2C%20they%20aren't%20removed%20for%20a%20certain%20period%20even%20after%20you%20have%20deleted%20the%20Gemini%20Apps%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20the%20conversations%20are%20kept%20separate%20and%20aren't%20connected%20to%20any%20user's%20Google%20Account.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20informed%20that%20the%20conversations%2C%20which%20may%20include%20your%20confidential%20information%2C%20are%20retained%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CConversations%20that%20have%20been%20reviewed%20or%20annotated%20by%20human%20reviewers%20(and%20related%20data%20like%20your%20language%2C%20device%20type%2C%20location%20info%2C%20or%20feedback)%20are%20not%20deleted%20when%20you%20delete%20your%20Gemini%20Apps%20activity%20because%20they%20are%20kept%20separately%20and%20are%20not%20connected%20to%20your%20Google%20Account.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20retained%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20further%2C%20it%20revealed%20that%20even%20after%20the%20Gemini%20Apps%20Activity%20is%20off%2C%20the%20user's%20conversation%20will%20be%20saved%20in%20their%20account%20for%20up%20to%2072%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20Gemini%20Apps%20Activity%20is%20off%2C%20your%20conversations%20will%20be%20saved%20with%20your%20account%20for%20up%20to%2072%20hours.%20This%20lets%20Google%20provide%20the%20service%20and%20process%20any%20feedback.%20This%20activity%20won't%20appear%20in%20your%20Gemini%20Apps%20Activity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Gemini%20can%20be%20activated%20with%20voice%20activation%2C%20even%20when%20you%20don't%20intend%20to.%C2%A0The%20blog%20clarified%2C%20%E2%80%9CGemini%20may%20activate%20when%20you%20didn't%20intend%20it%20to%2C%20for%20example%2C%20if%20there's%20a%20noise%20that%20sounds%20like%20%E2%80%9CHey%20Google.%E2%80%9D%20If%20this%20happens%20and%20Gemini%20responds%2C%20it%20will%20be%20treated%20the%20same%20as%20an%20intended%20activation%20and%20according%20to%20your%20settings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707804300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fl3io0a68_google-generic_625x300_11_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20has%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20all%20Android%20and%20iPhone%20users%2C%20regarding%20the%20potential%20security%20and%20privacy%20risks%20associated%20with%20the%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20smartphone%20apps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Aspirant%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Kota%20Hostel%20Day%20After%20JEE%20Mains%20Result%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20the%20disturbing%20series%20of%20student%20suicides%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Kota%2C%20an%20IIT%20aspirant%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20his%20hostel%20room%20this%20morning