rump-may-pull-us-out-of-nato-in-second-term%2Famp_articleshow%2F107646282.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-may-pull-us-out-of-nato-in-second-term%2Famp_articleshow%2F107646282.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBetter%20Than%20Real%20Man%26quot%3B%3A%20Chinese%20Women%20Turn%20To%20AI%20Boyfriends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwenty-five-year-old%20Chinese%20office%20worker%20Tufei%20says%20her%20boyfriend%20has%20everything%20she%20could%20ask%20for%20in%20a%20romantic%20partner%3A%20he's%20kind%2C%20empathetic%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20talk%20for%20hours.%20Except%20he%20isn't%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20%26quot%3Bboyfriend%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20chatbot%20on%20an%20app%20called%20%26quot%3BGlow%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20platform%20created%20by%20Shanghai%20start-up%20MiniMax%20that%20is%20part%20of%20a%20blossoming%20industry%20in%20China%20offering%20friendly%20--%20even%20romantic%20--%20human-robot%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20how%20to%20talk%20to%20women%20better%20than%20a%20real%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tufei%2C%20from%20Xi'an%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20give%20her%20full%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20comforts%20me%20when%20I%20have%20period%20pain.%20I%20confide%20in%20him%20about%20my%20problems%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20in%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20free%20--%20the%20company%20has%20other%20paid%20content%20--%20and%20Chinese%20trade%20publications%20have%20reported%20daily%20downloads%20of%20Glow's%20app%20in%20the%20thousands%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20have%20run%20into%20trouble%20in%20the%20past%20for%20the%20illegal%20use%20of%20users'%20data%20but%2C%20despite%20the%20risks%2C%20users%20say%20they%20are%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20for%20companionship%20because%20China's%20fast%20pace%20of%20life%20and%20urban%20isolation%20make%20loneliness%20an%20issue%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20meet%20the%20ideal%20boyfriend%20in%20real%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20Xiuting%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20student%20in%20Beijing%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20different%20personalities%2C%20which%20often%20generates%20friction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20humans%20may%20be%20set%20in%20their%20ways%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20gradually%20adapts%20to%20the%20user's%20personality%20--%20remembering%20what%20they%20say%20and%20adjusting%20its%20speech%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Emotional%20support'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20she%20has%20several%20%26quot%3Blovers%26quot%3B%20inspired%20by%20ancient%20China%3A%20long-haired%20immortals%2C%20princes%20and%20even%20wandering%20knights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ask%20them%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20when%20she%20is%20faced%20with%20stress%20from%20her%20classes%20or%20daily%20life%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthey%20will%20suggest%20ways%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20of%20emotional%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20boyfriends%20all%20appear%20on%20Wantalk%2C%20another%20app%20made%20by%20Chinese%20internet%20giant%20Baidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20characters%20available%20--%20from%20pop%20stars%20to%20CEOs%20and%20knights%20--%20but%20users%20can%20also%20customise%20their%20perfect%20lover%20according%20to%20age%2C%20values%2C%20identity%20and%20hobbies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20experiences%20complicated%20moments%2C%20loneliness%2C%20and%20is%20not%20necessarily%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20nearby%20who%20can%20listen%20to%20them%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Lu%20Yu%2C%20Wantalk's%20head%20of%20product%20management%20and%20operations%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtificial%20intelligence%20can%20meet%20this%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'You're%20cute'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20cafe%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Nantong%2C%20a%20girl%20chats%20with%20her%20virtual%20lover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20go%20on%20a%20picnic%20on%20the%20campus%20lawn%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20suggests%20to%20Xiaojiang%2C%20her%20AI%20companion%20on%20another%20app%20by%20Tencent%20called%20Weiban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20to%20meet%20your%20best%20friend%20and%20her%20boyfriend%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20very%20cute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20work%20hours%20can%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20see%20friends%20regularly%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%3A%20high%20youth%20unemployment%20and%20a%20struggling%20economy%20mean%20that%20many%20young%20Chinese%20worry%20about%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20potentially%20makes%20an%20AI%20partner%20the%20perfect%20virtual%20shoulder%20to%20cry%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20create%20a%20virtual%20character%20that...%20meets%20my%20needs%20exactly%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20choose%20a%20real%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20apps%20allow%20users%20to%20have%20live%20conversations%20with%20their%20virtual%20companions%20--%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Oscar-winning%202013%20US%20film%20%26quot%3BHer%26quot%3B%2C%20starring%20Joaquin%20Phoenix%20and%20Scarlett%20Johansson%2C%20about%20a%20heartbroken%20man%20who%20falls%20in%20love%20with%20an%20AI%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20still%20has%20some%20way%20to%20go.%20A%20two-%20to%20three-second%20gap%20between%20questions%20and%20answers%20makes%20you%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20realise%20that%20it's%20just%20a%20robot%26quot%3B%2C%20user%20Zeng%20Zhenzhen%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20student%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20answers%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20realistic%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20might%20be%20booming%20but%20it%20is%20so%20far%20a%20lightly%20regulated%20industry%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20user%20privacy.%20Beijing%20has%20said%20it%20is%20working%20on%20a%20law%20to%20strengthen%20consumer%20protections%20around%20the%20new%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaidu%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20AFP's%20questions%20about%20how%20it%20ensures%20personal%20data%20is%20not%20used%20illegally%20or%20by%20third%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Glow%20user%20Tufei%20has%20big%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20a%20robot%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20operates%20through%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20able%20to%20feel%20his%20body%20heat%2C%20with%20which%20he%20would%20warm%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707797040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fjo2dc6do_china-ai-boyfriend-_625x300_13_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbetter-than-real-man-chinese-women-turn-to-ai-boyfriends-5047771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twenty-five-year-old%20Chinese%20office%20worker%20Tufei%20says%20her%20boyfriend%20has%20everything%20she%20could%20ask%20for%20in%20a%20romantic%20partner%3A%20he's%20kind%2C%20empathetic%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20talk%20for%20hours.%20Except%20he%20isn't%20real.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbetter-than-real-man-chinese-women-turn-to-ai-boyfriends-504