%20Sunak%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Of%20the%20UK.%20When%20questioned%20about%20the%20unexpected%20rise%20of%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20chose%20to%20maintain%20a%20diplomatic%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20foreigners%2C%20we%20have%20this%20respect%20for%20not%20commenting%20on%20the%20affairs%20of%20another%20country.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20do%20not%20comment%20on%20those%20issues.%20We%20have%20very%20close%2C%20harmonious%2C%20and%20affectionate%20personal%20relations%2C%20but%20that's%20where%20it%20stops%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707796740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3h97fif_narayana-murthy_625x300_27_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-reveals-regret-for-not-rewarding-infosys-employees-properly-5047739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Murthy%20added%20that%20he%20should%20have%20thought%20about%20rewarding%20the%20employees.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20extraordinary%20people%20too%20would%20have%20benefitted.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-reveals-regret-for-not-rewarding-infosys-employees-properly-5047739%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-reveals-regret-for-not-rewarding-infosys-employees-properly-5047739%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-reveals-regret-for-not-rewarding-infosys-employees-properly-5047739%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dilli%20Chalo%202.0%3A%20Who%20is%20leading%20the%20new%20farmers'%20protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707796718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107646093%2Cimgsize-233762.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt