mpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Ftony-hale-beyonce-verizon-super-bowl-commercial-1235908580%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Ftony-hale-beyonce-verizon-super-bowl-commercial-1235908580%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20to%20Japan%20for%20a%203-week%20holiday.%20It's%20been%207%20years%20and%20I'm%20not%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20US%20anytime%20soon.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20hugging%20soft%20toy%20in%20a%20shop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c461c76fcb546d2d4d6330%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22867%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArianna%20Caiazzo%2C%2027%2C%20came%20to%20Japan%20as%20a%20teenager%20and%20has%20been%20living%20there%20since.%3Cp%3EArianna%20Caiazzo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EArianna%20Caiazzo%20went%20to%20Japan%20for%20a%20holiday%20after%20dropping%20out%20of%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Caiazzo%20now%20calls%20Japan%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20that%20life%20in%20Japan%20is%20more%20affordable%20and%20she%20feels%20safer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Arianna%20Caiazzo%2C%2027%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20Japan%20in%202017.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20salary%20and%20expenses.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20life%20in%20Japan%20started%20as%20a%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dropped%20out%20of%20college%20at%2019%20in%20my%20second%20year.%20My%20major%20in%20English%20at%20Arcadia%20University%20in%20Pennsylvania%20didn't%20seem%20like%20the%20right%20fit.%20I%20wanted%20to%20transfer%20to%20fashion%20school%2C%20but%20I%20missed%20the%20application%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20fascinated%20with%20Japan%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20especially%20its%20Harajuku%20fashion%2C%20which%20is%20really%20colorful%20and%20artistic.%20After%20years%20of%20being%20depressed%20and%20dressing%20up%20in%20all%20black%2C%20Harajuku%20fashion%20became%20a%20way%20for%20me%20to%20express%20my%20joy.%20I%20was%20dressing%20up%20with%20rainbow-colored%20braids%20and%20rainbow%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221169%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20in%20colorful%20clothes%20and%20makeup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c463f16fcb546d2d4d6336%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22877%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaiazzo%20felt%20that%20Harajuku%20fashion%20allowed%20her%20to%20express%20her%20happiness.%3Cp%3EArianna%20Caiazzo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20fashion%20as%20a%20big%20pull%20factor%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20Japan%20for%20a%20three-week%20trip.%20My%20parents%20thought%3A%20She's%20not%20going%20to%20make%20it%2C%20she's%20going%20to%20come%20home%20crying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20my%20three%20weeks%20there%20doing%20all%20the%20touristy%20things.%20I%20had%20never%20been%20on%20my%20own%20before.%20I%20was%20traveling%20around%20Tokyo%20and%20hitting%20all%20the%20clubs%20%E2%80%94%20being%20able%20to%20drink%20at%2019%20without%20being%20carded%20was%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20three%20weeks%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20parents%20if%20I%20could%20stay%20another%20three%20weeks%20and%20slowly%20kept%20extending%20my%20time.%20I%20loved%20the%20culture%20in%20Japan.%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20%E2%80%94%20no%20one%20was%20looking%20at%20me%2C%20no%20one%20was%20talking%20to%20me%20or%20bothering%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20in%2C%20I%20called%20my%20parents%20again%20and%20said%3A%20I%20want%20to%20live%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20hardest%20things%20I%20have%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20temporarily%20left%20for%20the%20US%20to%20get%20a%20longer%20visa%20to%20stay%20in%20Japan%2C%20I%20picked%20a%20language%20school%20and%20a%20vocational%20school%20I%20wanted%20to%20enroll%20in%20to%20study%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttending%20language%20school%20in%20Japan%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20things%20I%20have%20done.%20I%20was%20the%20only%20person%20who%20wasn't%20Asian%2C%20and%20I%20was%20alone%20all%20the%20time%20because%20the%20other%20students%20all%20spoke%20Chinese%2C%20Vietnamese%2C%20or%20Korean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20learning%20environment%20was%20harsh%20%E2%80%94%20teachers%20screamed%20at%20us%20and%20were%20allowed%20to%20pour%20water%20on%20us.%20They%20would%20berate%20me%2C%20telling%20me%20I%20had%20gained%20weight%20or%20saying%20my%20hair%20color%20was%20ugly.%20I%20started%20having%20panic%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20I%20enrolled%20into%20fashion%20school%2C%20which%20was%20a%20different%20wild%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchoolwork%20was%20tough.%20We%20were%20creating%20and%20submitting%20one%20outfit%20per%20week.%20My%20classmates%20were%20passing%20out%20from%20not%20sleeping%20all%20week%20and%20working%20all%20night%20long.%20I%20was%20completely%20burnt%20out%20by%20the%20time%20I%20graduated%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20am%20in%20a%20state%20of%20ease%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20lifting%20her%20leg%20outside%20Japanese%20temple%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c465bc43bb77284ba4cf86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaiazzo%20says%20that%20the%20friends%20she%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20friends%20that%20are%20like%20family%20now.%3Cp%3EAriana%20Caiazzo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20I%20faced%20in%20both%20schools%2C%20I%20was%20having%20an%20amazing%20time%20outside%20class.%20I%20love%20the%20food%2C%20and%20the%20friends%20I%20have%20made%20are%20my%20family%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20especially%20appreciate%20the%20safety.%20Back%20home%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20I%20always%20felt%20scared%20anytime%20I%20was%20home%20alone.%20Here%2C%20I%20am%20in%20a%20state%20of%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%20convenient%20public%20transportation%20system%20was%20another%20big%20plus%20point%2C%20because%20I%20hated%20driving%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20here%20also%20feels%20a%20lot%20more%20affordable.%20I%20can%20spend%20%2420%20for%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20groceries.%20I%20am%20still%20shocked%20that%2020%20eggs%20cost%20%242.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20with%20ADHD%20and%20Autism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20and%20Autism%20after%20I%20moved%20to%20Japan.%20ADHD%20medication%20is%20easily%20accessible%20here.%20I%20have%20to%20take%20five%20medicines%2C%20which%20only%20add%20up%20to%20about%20%24100%20per%20month%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20treatments%20are%20also%20cheaper%20%E2%80%94%20I%20went%20for%20eight%20Transcranial%20Magnetic%20Stimulation%20sessions%20in%20the%20span%20of%20one%20month%2C%20which%20was%20recommended%20for%20my%20symptoms.%20A%20set%20of%20treatments%20in%20the%20US%20would%20be%20%246%2C000.%20I%20pay%20%242%2C000%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20currently%20live%20in%20Osaka%2C%20and%20am%20renting%20an%20apartment%20with%20my%20boyfriend%20of%20four%20years.%20I%20teach%20English%20and%20math%20to%20six-%20to%20eight-year-olds%20at%20an%20after-school%20service.%20I%20work%20three%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20job%20more%20accessible%20with%20my%20health%20conditions%20than%20a%20career%20in%20fashion%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20pays%20me%203%2C000%20Japanese%20Yen%2C%20or%20about%20%2420%2C%20an%20hour.%20I%20am%20able%20to%20make%20about%20%241%2C340%20a%20month%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20I%20would%20get