%20yield%20a%20consensus%2C%20even%20though%20it%20continued%20past%2011%20pm.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20announced%20they%20will%20go%20ahead%20with%20their%20scheduled%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20march%20on%20February%2013%20at%2010%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20food%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20agriculture%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20meeting%20that%20went%20for%20close%20to%20five%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20government%20was%20not%20serious%20about%20any%20of%20their%20demands%20including%20legalising%20the%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%2C%20withdrawing%20criminal%20cases%20filed%20during%20the%202020%20farm%20protest%2C%20a%20farm%20loan%20waiver%20and%20several%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20just%20trying%20to%20prolong%20the%20matter%20by%20forming%20some%20committees%20despite%20our%20hope%20for%20some%20positive%20outcome.%20Hence%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20march%20towards%20Delhi%20as%20planned%20tomorrow%20at%2010%20am%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dallewal%2C%20flanked%20by%20other%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders.%20Around%20200%20farm%20union%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20SKM%20(non%20political)%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20(KMSC)%20are%20leading%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMSC%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20too%20said%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20go%20Delhi%20tomorrow%20as%20planned.%20The%20government%20did%20not%20have%20any%20proposals.%20We%20hoped%20that%20the%20discussion%20with%20the%20ministers%20would%20bring%20some%20conclusion%20in%20our%20favour.%20But%20nothing%20concrete%20came%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20the%20government%20calls%20for%20talks%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we%20will%20go.%20But%20our%20march%20stands.%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Union%20minister%20Munda%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20serious%20discussion%20with%20the%20farmers%20on%20every%20topic.%20The%20government%20wants%20to%20bring%20every%20solution%20through%20talks%E2%80%A6%20We%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20some%20topics.%20But%20there%20were%20some%20topics%20for%20which%20we%20said%20that%20a%20committee%20should%20be%20made%20for%20a%20permanent%20solution%E2%80%A6%20Any%20problem%20can%20be%20solved%20with%20discussion.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20we%20will%20bring%20solutions%E2%80%A6%20Our%20motive%20is%20that%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20public%20are%20protected%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20major%20contention%20was%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20enacting%20an%20MSP%20law.%20While%20the%20Union%20government%20was%20asking%20for%20a%20committee%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20did%20not%20agree.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Union%20did%20not%20make%20any%20commitment%20on%20a%20loan%20waiver.%20Dallewal%20told%20the%20media%20that%20several%20committees%20on%20the%20issue%20had%20already%20advocated%20the%20need%20to%20legalise%20the%20MSP.%20So%20another%20committee%20would%20have%20served%20no%20purpose.%20The%20Union%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20also%20not%20serious%20on%20a%20loan%20waiver%2C%20even%20as%20it%20waived%20off%20lakhs%20of%20crores%20of%20bad%20debt%20for%20big%20corporates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20block%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20being%20watched%20keenly%20since%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-ruled%20Haryana%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-farmers-head-to-delhi-for-protest-haryana-govt-creates-hurdles-on-their-path%5C%22%3Esealed%20its%20borders%20with%20Punjab%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20as%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat