tured%20a%20lot%20of%20shirtless%20dancing%20from%20Gronkowski's%20brother%20Chris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20hour%20four%20of%20Gronk%20Beach%20that%20my%20boyfriend%20turned%20to%20me%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20Chippendales%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20mere%20feet%20from%20the%20stage%20at%20Rob%20Gronkowski's%20annual%20Super%20Bowl%20party%2C%20where%20his%20shirtless%20brother%20Chris%20was%20dancing%20and%20flexing%20his%20muscles%20as%20the%20crowd%20cheered%20him%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scene%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20fitting%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGronk%20Beach%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20Super%20Bowl%20pre-parties.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rob%20Gronkowski%20parties%20onstage%20at%20Gronk%20Beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63f3a0b57b15f100194d2d4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERob%20Gronkowski%20parties%20onstage%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EMark%20Peterman%2FInvision%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGronkowski%20launched%20the%20first%20edition%20of%20Gronk%20Beach%20in%20Miami%20in%202020%20and%20brought%20it%20back%20last%20year%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-gronk-beach-super-bowl-party-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eparty%20in%20Scottsdale%2C%20Arizona%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20matchup%20between%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs%20and%20Philadelphia%20Eagles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGronk%20Beach%20is%20among%20a%20slate%20of%20Super%20Bowl%20parties%20produced%20by%20Medium%20Rare%2C%20which%20also%20hosted%20Shaquille%20O'Neal%20and%20Guy%20Fieri's%20events%20in%20Sin%20City.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20one-day%20event%20featured%20a%20lineup%20of%20performances%2C%20including%20a%20surprise%20Flo%20Rida%20set.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flo%20Rida%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%20Las%20Vegas%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca69366e2e190e71a39dce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlo%20Rida%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EMedium%20Rare%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDante%2C%20DJ%20Irie%2C%20and%20Afrojack%20also%20performed%20during%20the%20five-hour%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20entire%20Gronkowski%20family%20was%20in%20attendance.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rob%20Gronkowki%20and%20his%20family%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6c4a94aa8ee8e84a3996%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221463%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERob%20Gronkowski%20with%20his%20dad%20and%20four%20brothers%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EMindy%20Small%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeegan-Michael%20Key%2C%20Joey%20Fatone%2C%20and%20former%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20contestants%20Dale%20Moss%20and%20Hannah%20Godwin%20were%20among%20the%20celebrities%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGeneral%20admission%20tickets%20started%20at%20%2475%2C%20while%20VIP%20tables%20began%20at%20%247%2C500.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca695694aa8ee8e84a3847%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221271%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20guests%20were%20wearing%20%26quot%3BGronked%26quot%3B%20hats%20at%20the%20event%20in%20tribute%20to%20Gronkowski.%20%3Cp%3EMindy%20Small%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20guest%20I%20spoke%20to%20told%20me%20that%20prices%20were%20different%20for%20men%20and%20women%20(standard%20for%20the%20big%20Las%20Vegas%20clubs)%20and%20that%20her%20ticket%20cost%20%2475%20while%20her%20husband%20paid%20%24125.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ticket%20prices%20were%20cheaper%20than%20Gronk%20Beach%202023%2C%20which%20started%20at%20%24199%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20this%20year%2C%20they%20didn't%20come%20with%20unlimited%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20I%20was%20given%20my%20lei%2C%20a%20Gronk%20Beach%20staple%2C%20I%20made%20my%20way%20through%20Encore%20Beach%20Club.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%20crowd%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6b1e94aa8ee8e84a3941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGuests%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEncore%20Beach%20Club%C2%A0has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20Las%20Vegas%20day%20clubs%20since%20it%20opened%20in%202010.%20I%20was%20extremely%20dedicated%20to%20the%20Vegas%20party%20scene%20in%20my%2020s%20since%20it's%20only%20a%20four-hour%20drive%20from%20LA%2C%20so%20walking%20through%20the%20pool%20area%20of%20%26quot%3BEBC%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20we've%20always%20called%20it%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0was%20weirdly%20nostalgic%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20was%20no%20regular%20Sin%20City%20pool%20party.%20Day-club%20season%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20doesn't%20usually%20kick%20off%20until%20mid-March%20due%20to%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20temperatures%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024%20were%20in%20the%20low%2050s.%20Most%20guests%20were%20casually%20dressed%20in%20jeans%20and%20their%20preferred%20team%20jersey%20(both%20of%20which%20are%20banned%20during%20a%20typical%20EBC%20pool%20party).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20few%20groups%20who%20brought%20out%20their%20sparkly%20Vegas%20best%2C%20but%20most%20people%20opted%20for%20comfort.%20Even%20Gronk%20stayed%20in%20his%20sweatshirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20club's%20pools%20were%20empty%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20despite%20being%20heated.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6ac094aa8ee8e84a38fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20pools%20at%20Encore%20Beach%20Club%20during%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20I%20saw%20someone%20enter%20one%20of%20the%20pools%20was%20when%20a%20man%20in%20jeans%20ran%20in%2C%20ankle-deep%2C%20to%20catch%20a%20flying%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20the%20casino%20pit%20at%20the%20bar%20was%20packed.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%20bar%20area%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6a976fcb546d2d4e9dee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20gambling%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEBC's%20craps%20and%20blackjack%20tables%20were%20brimming%20with%20energy%20as%20people%20yelped%20with%20joy%20over%20their%20wins%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20made%20my%20way%20to%20the%20main%20bar%2C%20where%20I%20was%20greeted%20with%20a%20giant%20shirtless%20painting%20of%20Gronk.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6b326e2e190e71a39eaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20bars%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20boyfriend%20Peter%20grabbed%20us%20drinks%20(%2445%20without%20tip%20for%20a%20rum%20and%20coke%20and%20vodka%20soda)%2C%20I%20chatted%20with%20a%20San%20Francisco%2049ers%20fan%20named%20Nikki%2C%20who%20was%20in%20town%20for%20her%20second%20Super%20Bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20to%20LA%20thinking%20it%20was%20a%20bucket%20list%20sort%20of%20thing%2C%20and%20then%20they%20announced%202024%20was%20going%20to%20be%20in%20Vegas%2C%20and%20we%20went%2C%20'Well%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%2C'%26quot%3B%20Nikki%20told%20me%2C%20revealing%20she%20bought%20her%20Super%20Bowl%20ticket%20in%20May%20for%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20got%20lucky%20that%20my%20team%20made%20it%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENikki%20said%20her%20experience%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bway%20better%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Super%20Bowl%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%2C%20it's%20been%20nice%20because%20everything's%20so%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me%2C%20adding%20that%20Gronk%20Beach%20was%20the%20only%20pre-party%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20decided%20to%20attend%20because%20none%20of%20the%20other%20events%20%26quot%3Breally%20spoke%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20has%20been%20the%20case%20throughout%20the%20NFL%20football%20season%2C%20the%20conversation%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-football-outfits-are-huge-for-fashion-brands-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Nikki%20said%20she's%20glad%20the%20singer%20is%20bringing%20%26quot%3Bdads%20and%20teenage%20daughters%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20that%20she's%20found%20herself%20an%20all-American%20golden%20retriever%20boyfriend%20rather%20than%20the%20moody%20artists%20she%20was%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Nikki%20added%20with%20a%20laugh%2C%20noting%20that%20all%20her%20girlfriends%20were%20hoping%20she'd%20see%20Swift%20in%20Vegas%20that%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20we%20headed%20to%20the%20dance%20floor%20to%20catch%20Flo%20Rida's%20surprise%20set.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flo%20Rida%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6ca494aa8ee8e84a39af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlo%20Rida%20sings%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EMedium%20Rare%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20must%20have%20been%20packed%20with%20millennials%20because%20the%20singalong%20energy%20was%20extremely%20strong%20as%20Flo%20Rida%20tore%20through%20his%20biggest%20mid-2010%20hits%20while%20fake%20bills%20rained%20down%20on%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%2016%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20Peter%20as%20everyone%20screamed%2C%20%26quot%3BBoots%20with%20the%20fur%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Flo%20Rida%20sang%20%26quot%3BLow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20dance%20floor%20was%20surrounded%20by%20bottle-service%20tables.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6b5b94aa8ee8e84a394d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDon%20Julio%20and%20Dom%20P%C3%A9rignon%20at%20one%20of%20the%20tables.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20center%20of%20the%20dance%20floor%20was%20gated%20off%20for%20VIP%20tables%2C%20you%20could%20still%20get%20surprisingly%20close%20to%20the%20stage%20with%20a%20GA%20ticket%2C%20and%20there%20was%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20much%20better%20deal%20than%20Shaq's%20Fun%20House%20the%20night%20before%2C%20where%20a%20%24150%20ticket%20only%20got%20you%20outdoor%20