20Skewer%20was%20my%20favorite%20food%20item%2C%20and%20at%20%241%2C%20it's%20also%20the%20cheapest%20item%20on%20the%20entire%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20consists%20of%20three%20different%20flavored%20mini%20doughnuts%20held%20together%20through%20an%20orange%20skewer.%20The%20flavors%20I%20got%20were%20classic%20glazed%2C%20chocolate%20glazed%2C%20and%20one%20that%20tasted%20as%20if%20it%20was%20spiced%20with%20cinnamon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20found%20the%20skewer%20unnecessary%20as%20the%20mini%20doughnuts%20fell%20off%20after%20one%20bite%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20see%20the%20point%20in%20sticking%20the%20skewer%20into%20any%20of%20the%20drinks%20I%20ordered%2C%20I%20loved%20how%20light%20the%20texture%20of%20each%20little%20ball%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20all%20had%20a%20crispy%2C%20glazed%2C%20iced%20exterior%20but%20were%20perfectly%20fluffy%20and%20a%20good%20portioned%20snack%20to%20have%20along%20with%20a%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20The%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca673c6e2e190e71a39cc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee.%3Cp%3EThe%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dunkin'%20Donuts%2C%20the%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee%20is%20Affleck's%20go-to%20drink%20order.%20After%20trying%20it%20myself%2C%20I%20get%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%243.29%2C%20it's%20the%20most%20expensive%20drink%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20it%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20a%20sweet%20tooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beverage%20features%20unsweetened%20vanilla%20flavoring%2C%20french%20vanilla%20swirl%20syrup%2C%20cream%2C%20sweet%20cold%20foam%2C%20cinnamon%20sugar%2C%20and%20regular%20whole%20milk.%20The%20cinnamon%20sugar%20added%20a%20much-needed%20twist%20t