ages%20with%20which%20I%20convincingly%20disagree%20on%20factual%20and%20moral%20grounds.%20Me%20lending%20my%20voice%20to%20them%20could%20constitute%20a%20constitutional%20travesty%2C%20hence%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20House%2C%20I%20conclude%20my%20address.%20Wish%20this%20House%20a%20productive%20and%20healthy%20discussion%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20people.%20Vaazhga%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Vaazhaga%20Bharatam%2C%20Jai%20Hind%2C%20Jai%20Bharat%2C%20Nandri%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20added%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Ftn-governor-ravi-dmk-regime-not-respecting-national-anthem-9156907%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20governor%20alleged%20that%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20had%20repeatedly%20ignored%20his%20request%20to%20play%20the%20national%20anthem%20before%20and%20after%20the%20address.%20He%20underlined%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cshow%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20national%20anthem%E2%80%9D.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-guv-rn-ravi-refuses-to-read-customary-speech-in-assembly-on-moral-grounds%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20a%20custom%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20to%20sing%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20%E2%80%98Tamil%20Thai%20Vazhthu%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20song%20of%20praise%20to%20the%20Tamil%20language%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Assembly%20sessions%20and%20end%20the%20session%20with%20national%20anthem.%20%C2%A0While%20Ravi%20refused%20to%20continue%20reading%20the%20c%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eustomary%20address%C2%A0prepared%20for%20him%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETamil%20Nadu%20assembly%20Speaker%20M.%20Appavu%20read%20out%20the%20Tamil%20version%20of%20the%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20speaker%20made%20certain%20remarks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Ravi%20left%20with%20his%20staff%20even%20after%20the%20speaker%20reminded%20him%20in%20Tamil%20that%20the%20national%20anthem%20was%20to%20be%20played.%20The%20members%20in%20treasury%20and%20opposition%20benches%2C%20including%20BJP%20MLAs%2C%20remained%20in%20the%20Assembly%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20session.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20episode%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20budget%20session%2C%20Ravi%20omitted%20portions%20on%20Ambedkar%2C%20Dravidian%20leaders%2C%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20governance%20and%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20from%20his%20speech.%20This%20gesture%20was%20condemned%20by%20the%20Stalin-led%20government.%20Further%2C%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20moved%20a%20resolution%20which%20irked%20the%20governor%20and%20he%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Assembly%20before%20the%20national%20anthem%20was%20played%20in%20the%20end%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-governor-skips-portions-dravidian-leaders-and-ambedkar-speech-cm-objects-171717%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EPast%20conflicts%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20protested%20against%20Ravi%20as%20the%3Cem%3E%20PTI%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-politics%2Ftamil-nadu-vs-tamilagam-governor-rn-ravi-row-dmk-8368892%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHere%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20narrative%20has%20been%20created.%20Everything%20applicable%20for%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20say%20no.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20habit.%20So%20many%20theses%20have%20been%20written%20%E2%80%93%20all%20false%20and%20poor%20fiction.%20This%20must%20be%20broken.%20Truth%20must%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Last%20year%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20governor%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20state%20administration%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Condriya%20arasu%E2%80%9D%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frn-ravi-dmk-tamil-term-union-govt-8376233%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707741059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F09203318%2FUntitled-design-6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftn-governor-abruptly-ends-customary-address-to-assembly-leaves-house-in-a-huff%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R.N.%20Ravi%20ended%20his%20speech%20abruptly%2C%20saying%20there%20are%20passages%20presented%20to%20him%20by%20the%20DMK%20government%20which%20he%20'convincingly%20disagree%20on%20factual%20and%20moral%20grounds'.%20He%20left%20the%20House%20without%20waiting%20for%20the%20National%20Anthem%20to%20be%20played.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftn-governor-abruptly-ends-customary-address-to-assembly-leaves-house-in-a-huff%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22National%20Student%20Innovation%20Challenge%3A%20This%20Competition%20Taps%20Into%20Young%20Talent%20To%20Solve%20Big%20Problems%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEducation%20must%20build%20character%2C%20enabling%20learners%20to%20be%20ethical%2C%2