%20LED%20TV.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20Rai%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineering%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20is%20a%20passionate%20runner%20with%20many%20ultra-marathons%20under%20his%20belt.%20Upon%20starting%20his%20career%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20juggle%20his%20job%20responsibilities%20with%20regular%20gym%20visits%20for%20strength%20training%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20runners.%20Residing%20in%20a%20rented%20accommodation%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20limited%20equipment%20at%20his%20disposal%20at%20home%20fell%20short%20of%20adequately%20supporting%20his%20training%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Dani%20also%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20find%20time%20to%20head%20to%20the%20gym%20due%20to%20long%20work%20hours.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rohit%20Patel%20and%20Amal%20George%2C%20who%20were%20studying%20robotics%2C%20spent%20hours%20building%20solutions%20for%20everyday%20problems%2C%20and%20were%20keen%20on%20solving%20this%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20really%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20no%20single%20equipment%20that%20could%20replicate%20the%20entire%20gym%20at%20home.%20They%20discovered%20that%20home%20gym%20equipment%20was%20big%2C%20costly%2C%20and%20demanded%20ample%20space.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20accurately%20monitor%20their%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20have%20to%20keep%20buying%20different%20weights%20and%20bars%20to%20train%20at%20home.%20This%20occupies%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20especially%20in%20rented%20spaces%20and%20small%20apartments.%20It%20also%20becomes%20bulky%20and%20unsafe.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20new%20digital-weights%20technology%20emerged.%20Amal%20and%20Rohit%2C%20robotics%20graduates%2C%20explored%20c