e%20%E2%80%98Aroleap%20Fitness%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99.%20Amid%20the%20pandemic%2C%20like%20most%20people%2C%20the%20founders%20headed%20home.%20Aman%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Anurag%20hail%20from%20Bhilai%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20have%20known%20each%20other%20since%20school.%20So%20they%20were%20able%20to%20continue%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298698%2Fflexnest-home-gym-equipment-fitness-startup-earns-millions-no-vc-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ER%26amp%3BD%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20winter%20of%202020%2C%20with%20their%20first%20prototype%20in%20hand%2C%20they%20initiated%20their%20first%20round%20of%20trials%20by%20inviting%20friends%20from%20school%20over.%20They%20filmed%20a%20video%20showcasing%20their%20product%20and%20commenced%20sharing%20it%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20get%20people%20interested%20in%20the%20product%2C%20we%20started%20by%20offering%20monthly%20subscriptions%2C%20priced%20equal%20to%20a%20premium%20gym%20membership.%20We%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20and%20once%20back%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20we%20sent%20our%20prototypes%20to%20a%20few%20people%20who%20seemed%20very%20interested%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20first%20customers%20tried%20the%20product%20for%20four%20to%20six%20months%20and%20offered%20their%20feedback%20to%20the%20founders.%20Based%20on%20the%20feedback%2C%20the%20engineers%20made%20changes%20to%20the%20product.%20Once%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20the%20product%2C%20they%20encountered%20the%20big%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20try%20their%20luck%2C%20Rohit%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20Nithin%20Kamath%2C%20CEO%20of%20Zerodha.%20Aman%20states%20that%20Nithin%20came%20to%20their%20apartment%20in%20J%20P%20Nagar%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20tried%20the%20prototype.%20Impressed%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20bet%20on%20them%20and%20become%20their%20first%20angel%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20found%20three%20other%20investors%20and%20raised%20their%20seed%20capital%20in%20October%202021.%20Then%2C%20they%20set%20up%20a%20small%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20began%20selling%20Aroleap%20X%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20home%20gym%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzYutqvSwlK%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Aroleap%20(%40aroleap)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAroleap%20X%20is%20a%20compact%2C%20wall-mounted%20smart%20exercise%20machine%20that%20uses%20motor-powered%20electromagnetic%20resistances%20to%20provide%20a%20dat